description: The Ginger Armadillo is not a BBQ truck, not a burger or a taco truck—but it might just be all those things. This Austin food truck can take quintessential Texas cuisine and give it a gourmet spin, or international dishes and give them a Texas spin. The menu changes monthly based on what’s local and in season, so you’ll never have to have the same thing twice... but you’ll want to!
name: The Ginger Armadillo
